  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* Add percentage for jobs option, fixes https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/issues/85\r\n* Update logic for exit on error option to exit after first command failure, fixes https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/issues/98\r\n* Bump libc from 0.2.184 to 0.2.185 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/pull/88\r\n* Bump bitflags from 2.11.0 to 2.11.1 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/pull/89\r\n* Bump tokio from 1.51.1 to 1.52.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/pull/90\r\n* Bump clap from 4.6.0 to 4.6.1 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/pull/91\r\n* Bump tokio from 1.52.0 to 1.52.1 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/pull/92\r\n* Bump assert_cmd from 2.2.0 to 2.2.1 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/pull/93\r\n* Bump libc from 0.2.185 to 0.2.186 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/pull/94\r\n* Bump tokio from 1.52.1 to 1.52.2 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/pull/95\r\n* Bump tokio from 1.52.2 to 1.52.3 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/pull/96\r\n* Bump assert_cmd from 2.2.1 to 2.2.2 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/pull/97\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/aaronriekenberg/rust-parallel/compare/v1.22.0...v1.23.0",
